ActFirearms Act
Subject2016 Can-Am Police and Fire Games Exemption Order - Thunder Bay, Ontario
Precis2016 CAN-AM POLICE -FIRE GAMES EXEMPTION ORDER which allows, subject to conditions and restrictions, prescribed individuals registered for shooting events at the upcoming Games to enter Canada with prohibited firearms and ammunition and transit to the Games, use these firearms during events, and exit Canada after the conclusion of the Games.
